    <content>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3" color="#FF0000"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;REGISTRATION IS NOW CLOSED FOR THIS EVEN&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;T:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; Confirmation emails have been sent to the first 30 participants. You can still register and leave a comment to this post below and you will be added to a waitlist.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam__;!!GF_29dbcQIUBPA!ywvFt4py1B3_IuUnpF-227A8WNSUvXyPt2KI03WB6h6Cb7Aq8seVA-43YXWHQncW6VnzteHJZvo3b2UpxVJHa0Xv6J3X-vx0$" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;event will give you a &lt;STRONG&gt;hands-on&lt;/STRONG&gt; experience with SAP Build for building apps and business processes without code (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Low Code/No Code&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;You will get to know the environment by creating:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business app for an online store (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Apps).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business process for approving purchases (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Process Automation).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business website (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Work Zone).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;You will get to know the&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build lobby&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;, where you access all your SAP Build artifacts, and get a deeper understanding of the following topics:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Apps&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Connecting to a backend service&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Building UIs&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Binding data&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Navigation&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Triggering processes from your app&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Deploy App to BTP&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Process Automation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Creating a process&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Adding approvals&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Creating actions&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Calling SAP backends (SAP S/4HANA Cloud and CAP services)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Updating data&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Conditions and GoTo flows&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Custom variables&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Work Zone(Standard Edition)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Create site&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Create page&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Create space&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Embed a Build App&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;Location&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;ROBERT BOSCH MIDDLE EAST FZE DAFZA&lt;/STRONG&gt;, Block A701,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;West wing 5 - Dubai Airport Free Zone - Dubai - United Arab Emirates&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;Maps: &lt;A href="https://eur03.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmaps.app.goo.gl%2F3m2NoFspYMKwHR889&amp;amp;data=05%7C02%7Cshrinivasan.neelamegam%40sap.com%7C3586c5d6897e4a22258c08dd4b2ee69f%7C42f7676cf455423c82f6dc2d99791af7%7C0%7C0%7C638749387004330631%7CUnknown%7CTWF