/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;@eshrinivasan&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Please note that spaces are limited to&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;30&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;If you want to attend, register by clicking the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Yes&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;button in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Will you be attending?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;section.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Bring your own laptop with power adapter and have a supported Web browser such as Google Chrome or Firefox installed on your laptop.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT face="arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Complete these SAP Build &lt;STRONG&gt;prerequisites&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;before&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;you come to the event:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/developers.sap.com/tutorials/codejam-0-prerequisites.html__;!!GF_29dbcQIUBPA!ywvFt4py1B3_IuUnpF-227A8WNSUvXyPt2KI03WB6h6Cb7Aq8seVA-43YXWHQncW6VnzteHJZvo3b2UpxVJHa0Xv6Ma3QOYW$" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Set Up Prerequisites for SAP Build CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</content>
