    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/sap-build-create-apps-processes-and-sites-without-code-kuala-lumpur/ev-p/14112261</id>
    <title>🇲🇾 SAP Build: Create Apps, Processes and Sites Without Code (Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia)</title>
    <updated>2025-05-27T08:08:27.635000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>eshrinivasan</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This is the all-new and revised&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;event for&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;low-code/no-code tooling and will give you a hands-on experience with SAP Build for building apps, business processes, and business sites without coding.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;You will get to know the environment by creating:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business app for an online store (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Apps&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business process for approving purchases (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Process Automation&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;An apps landing page&amp;nbsp;(&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Work Zone, standard edition&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color="#000000"&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Bring your own laptop with power adapter and have a supported Web browser such as Google Chrome or Firefox installed on your laptop.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;It can be helpful to bring a tablet or second laptop, if you have.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Complete these prerequisites BEFORE you come:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/codejam-0-prerequisites.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Set Up Prerequisites for SAP Build CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Location and Date:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This is an&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;in-person&lt;/STRONG&gt; event&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;only&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;(not virtual) and is planned for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Monday,&amp;nbsp;July 7th, 2025&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;from&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;09:00 - 16:00 local time &lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;(MYT)&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt; in&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;. The language of the event and the content will be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;English&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Event Address:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Malaysia&amp;nbsp; Sdn Bhd, Level 29, Menara Southpoint, Medan Syed Putra Selatan, Mid Valley City, 59200 Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Google maps location: &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/VNhfzRZ1om3KBNtX6" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://maps.app.goo.gl/VNhfzRZ1om3KBNtX6&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The instructors are SAP Developer Advocates &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/142394"&gt;@sheenamk&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298"&gt;@eshrinivasan&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Thank you &lt;STRONG&gt;Mark9&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;Solutions&lt;/STRONG&gt; for hosting this event.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Please note that spaces are limited!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;We can only accommodate&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;30&lt;/STRONG&gt; attendees&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;If you want to attend, register by clicking the&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Yes&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;button in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Will you be attending?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;section above to the right. A few weeks before the event, we will ask you to confirm your attendance.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/sap-build-create-apps-processes-and-sites-without-code-kuala-lumpur/ev-p/14112261"/>
    <published>2025-05-27T08:08:27.635000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/getting-started-with-generative-ai-hub-on-sap-ai-core-bangkok-thailand/ev-p/14112276</id>
    <title>🇹🇭 Getting started with Generative AI Hub on SAP AI Core (Bangkok, Thailand)</title>
    <updated>2025-05-27T08:16:21.162000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>eshrinivasan</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;event is on&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Getting Started with Generative AI Hub on SAP AI Core&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;and Python. You do not need any background in the topic, but you should have&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;a lot of curiosity!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;In this CodeJam, you will learn how to use the Generative AI Hub on SAP AI Core to implement &lt;STRONG&gt;retrieval-augmented generation&lt;/STRONG&gt; (RAG). This approach improves the responses of large language models (LLMs) and &lt;STRONG&gt;reduces hallucinations&lt;/STRONG&gt;. You will learn how to &lt;STRONG&gt;deploy an LLM&lt;/STRONG&gt; and the &lt;STRONG&gt;orchestration service&lt;/STRONG&gt; on SAP AI Core, and how to query it via SAP AI Launchpad and the Python SDK. Additionally, you will gain insights into key generative AI concepts and learn how to enhance RAG responses.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;Location and Date:&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This is a free&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;in-person event&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;only&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;(not virtual) and is planned for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Monday,&amp;nbsp;July 9th, 2025&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;from&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;10:00 - 15:30&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;hrs local time (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;ICT)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt; in&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Bangkok, Thailand&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;. The language of the event and the content will be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;English&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Event Address:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Thailand Ltd&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;, Park Silom, Si Lom, Khet Bang Rak, Krung Thep Maha Nakhon 10500, Thailand&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;. &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Google maps location: &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://eur03.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmaps.app.goo.gl%2FFkbF9fr4VwHKkrjK8&amp;amp;data=05%7C02%7Cshrinivasan.neelamegam%40sap.com%7C9c6221c2044f4041dca208dd9c0f2aa3%7C42f7676cf455423c82f6dc2d99791af7%7C0%7C0%7C638838311153835445%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;amp;sdata=sQt%2Bdd4OfbXpu9lwjH9K8FrW5cKiHqSAX5zmBbZB6i0%3D&amp;amp;reserved=0" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;https://maps.app.goo.gl/FkbF9fr4VwHKkrjK8&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The instructors are SAP Developer Advocates &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/142394"&gt;@sheenamk&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298"&gt;@eshrinivasan&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The event is kindly hosted by &lt;STRONG&gt;Mark9 Solutions&lt;/STRONG&gt;. Thank you!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Prerequisites:&amp;nbsp;Any Chromium-based web browser, such as Vivaldi, Brave, Microsoft Edge, Google Chrome etc.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="4"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Please note that spaces are limited!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;We can only accommodate&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;30&lt;/STRONG&gt; attendees&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;If you want to attend, register by clicking the&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Yes&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;button in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Will you be attending?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;section above to the right. A few weeks before the event, we will ask you to confirm your attendance.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
